---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Articles" currentPath="/blog/articles">
  <div class="section-nav">
    <a href="/blog">Blog Overview</a>
    <a href="/blog/articles" class="active">Articles List</a>
  </div>

  <article>
    <h1>All Articles</h1>
    <p>Read detailed articles written to help musicians understand the neurology, ergonomics, and daily practice of focal dystonia recovery.</p>
    
    <div style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <article style="margin-bottom: 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        <h3><a href="/blog/articles/musicians-focal-hand-dystonia-what-you-need-to-know">Musician's focal hand dystonia - what you need to know</a></h3>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem;">An essential primer covering diagnosis, neurological mechanisms, and standard vs. alternative recovery options.</p>
      </article>

      <article style="margin-bottom: 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        <h3><a href="/blog/articles/insights-fhd-resolution">Some insights in F(H)D resolution (January-June 2016)</a></h3>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem;">Key findings and practical observations gained from six months of intensive client retraining sessions.</p>
      </article>

      <article style="margin-bottom: 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        <h3><a href="/blog/articles/understanding-focal-dystonia-thailand-guitar-society">'Understanding Focal Dystonia' - my presentation to the Thailand Guitar Society</a></h3>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem;">A summary of the talk given to guitarists in Thailand regarding early symptoms, prevention, and retraining fundamentals.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
